GLOSSARY:
LWSS    Light weight Spaceship
MWSS    Medium weight Spaceship

TO NOTE:
:p stands for period. The time it takes an oscillator to regain its first form.
:c stands for "speed of light". The maximum possible speed of any moving pattern.

Speed:
The glider takes 4 generations to move one cell diagonally      v = c/4
The LWSS takes 2 generations to move one cell orthogonally      v = c/2

